# IDE - VS Code
.vscode/

# 1. Ignore all files inside the dags folder
dags/*

# 2. But do NOT ignore the dags folder itself
!dags/

# 3. Do NOT ignore files starting with prod_
!dags/prod_*

# 4. Do NOT ignore subdirectories if you want to keep them
!dags/*/